definitions.definition: ( medicine ) Excessive sensitivity to light and the aversion to bright light; abnormal fear of light.

main_definition: ( medicine ) Excessive sensitivity to light and the aversion to bright light; abnormal fear of light.

definitions.definition: An aversion to or fear of being photographed , the dissemination of personal photographs, or viewing photographs.

main_definition: An aversion to or fear of being photographed , the dissemination of personal photographs, or viewing photographs.
